         <abstract id="aspace_1864ce93561f62503c0ecf7be45a0563">The German Poster and Postcard Collection consists of approximately 2400 posters and 150 postcards from East and West Germany depicting countercultural, political, and propaganda themes from the 1970s to 1990. A small number of newspapers and pamphlets are included in the collection.</abstract>
